{
  "stem": "4753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my brother said he is not joining of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of them said-- later, I tried to take my brother out from Hungary when I finally found out he is alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I did go to the Swedish king to ask permission for my brother, visiting permission, to come just to see him once.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he did the paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, the Hungarians made him pay a lot of money, luxury, and so on, for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] airplane ticket and everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they told him that you will never leave the Hungary alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they took him off of the plane.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They let him go so far to sit on the plane.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, they took him off and told him you will not leave Hungary ever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they kept their word, because later one of the Hungarian communists in my city watched for him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The irony is that he did go to that few Jews who returned to the city to [SIGHS] [SOBBING] go to the temple to pray for the dead who died in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as he was going, one of the Hungarian communists hit him with a truck purposely, and he died.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So his grave is in my city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mine-- that's not mine anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That's what happened to my older brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told you that I had an older sister and a younger brother, also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then my-- my sister did work for a Christian company.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was a buyer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And three days later, as the Germans occupied Hungary-- that was March 19, 1944-- she was sent to Budapest by her boss.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she never did return.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The SS-- German SS-- with the Hungarian soldiers' help, or police help, took her off from the train.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
